{"tid":2262123,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"睇樓想還價要俾票先","createTime":"2020-10-29T00:00:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T02:33:36.000Z","uid":242771,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d172c22e8216eb7b94160393600ffd9292c0ebc0","tid":2262123,"uid":242771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T00:00:53.000Z","msg":"想請教下<br />\n如果我睇啱層樓想還價 AA叫我俾票簽臨約等佢同業主傾<br />\n<br />\n咁張票應該寫邊個？<br />\n同埋臨約就咁簽個名而唔寫定心目中個價<br />\n<br />\n風險咪好大？想睇下大家有咩實戰經驗同心得<br />\nthanks!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a913c3fa4f0f463c3be6ef674bc0e16f994fb90","tid":2262123,"uid":268,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T00:22:30.000Z","msg":"細行？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鋤價 臨約其實我不嬲都唔簽 多數淨比票<br />\n同埋點解要漏空個價？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n漏空緊係大風險 一定要寫埋你要還既價錢<br />\n<br />\n開票傾可以 而金額一般係寫你心目中價錢3%<br />\n或齊頭10萬 20萬都可以 呢樣就隨你<br />\n至於抬頭穩陣起見起碼寫上 律師 兩個字<br />\n前邊同最後邊都漏空 <br />\n因有啲係律師樓 有啲係事務所/行<br />\n比完再影低 <br />\n同埋簽埋恊議寫幾時之內要比返張票你"},{"pid":"c359306d67317622ec12ac56fcde58614c36c37d","tid":2262123,"uid":268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d172c22e8216eb7b94160393600ffd9292c0ebc0","tid":2262123,"uid":242771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T00:00:53.000Z","msg":"想請教下<br />\n如果我睇啱層樓想還價 AA叫我俾票簽臨約等佢同業主傾<br />\n<br />\n咁張票應該寫邊個？<br />\n同埋臨約就咁簽個名而唔寫定心目中個價<br />\n<br />\n風險咪好大？想睇下大家有咩實戰經驗同心得<br />\nthanks!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T00:26:42.000Z","msg":"有咩都寫清寫楚 白紙黑字保障自己<br />\n唔好同aa 口頭講個信字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a604989f507ee7b8cd77cdd933fe6ef8f819c8da","tid":2262123,"uid":38172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T00:35:48.000Z","msg":"多數寫律師樓 同埋基本上唔會拎去入 拎黎去講價叫做買家有誠意啲"},{"pid":"e578f2d11b8535ddda51dac98cebc687fc66c639","tid":2262123,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T00:36:48.000Z","msg":"上次我睇睇下樓，突然走去直接開口價<br />\n(業主及AA都在場)<br />\n<br />\nAA 個表情 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n驚死我同個業主傾掂數咁，即刻拉開我地去另一間房，跟住佢就穿梭買家賣家，出價還價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其間我鍾意點開價都得，最後成交到，事前冇簽任何臨約，冇交票<br />\n幾好玩，可以試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"307c0c60e9cfd40690ae243362f96f21f535acbd","tid":2262123,"uid":63108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T00:40:09.000Z","msg":"換Aa狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad5ef004ce75651fe68fed93b3e944e14586556","tid":2262123,"uid":263025,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"d172c22e8216eb7b94160393600ffd9292c0ebc0","tid":2262123,"uid":242771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T00:00:53.000Z","msg":"想請教下<br />\n如果我睇啱層樓想還價 AA叫我俾票簽臨約等佢同業主傾<br />\n<br />\n咁張票應該寫邊個？<br />\n同埋臨約就咁簽個名而唔寫定心目中個價<br />\n<br />\n風險咪好大？想睇下大家有咩實戰經驗同心得<br />\nthanks!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T00:42:21.000Z","msg":"呢個時候係香港買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你問大家風險？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你買得多樓仲問黎做乜，樓都買得，幾十萬算咩風險呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n等睇你供到退休比人共你個産。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n是日笑話: 有人响香港買樓。